mkdir = create Folder

touch = create Files

cd = get in the folder 

cd ../ = get out of the folder

clear = clear terminal

ls = list of the files and folders in one line horizontal way

ls -l = list of the files in vertical way

ls -la = list of all files including all hidden files in vertical way

rm = delete only files

rm -r = delete only folders

rm -rf * = delete all

* = all

mv = move (mv "files name" space "folder name")

cp = copy (cp "files name" space "new file name")

vim and nano are the softwares that can you in terminal.